Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one is my feel is the feel of addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And many times I've heard over the years that people who get into drugs and alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and become addicted are on a negative path looking for spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The second one, I run a program called Bridging the Gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one was it's a negative pathway, that's positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If it leads to God, it's hardly negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say it's the hard way to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see it also as a spiritual path, but the slow route, the slow boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Addiction is the way of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:00:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See, with addiction, you've got two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You either surrender to God or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't change your mind and get off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a progressive disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes you down to finally suicide, dementia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you either surrender to God or you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very strict pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The second question is that ever since I discovered your book,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to figure out how to incorporate the material into the program
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because we are holistically based and we're looking at a lot of different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,acu-detox and yoga and exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've really focused on the physiology of addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of addiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the biochemical aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're more in the physical along with the 12-step model and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you said a few minutes ago that half the population is below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't use that as far as kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So although my experience has been overall that drug addicts and alcoholics,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at least the ones that get to treatment, are usually above average,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at least the ones we treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The disease is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe you have to approach all three, including nutrition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,making sure they don't go into hypoglycemic relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just take them off sugar and sweets and put them on big doses of vitamins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and send them to AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've done what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But how would you specifically use what you speak of in a program?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any thoughts on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I send them to AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We do also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to say if they do the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the third step, you're surrendering everything to God as it arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,including resisting admitting the fact that you have an addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have our difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have one program that specializes in professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we get doctors, lawyers, and they don't tend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we have a mixture, but many of them will not go to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or do not want to incorporate anything to do with AA in their program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pridefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tell them, you've got humility in life or pride in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care which choice you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't give a damn whether you live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something to you, but to me, it's only a nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the zen of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spoken of intentions here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you explain the difference between goals and intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether or not the visualization process
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or how important the visualization process is to the fulfillment of goals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualization has to do with form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Form is not necessarily a spiritual goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a worldly goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A goal is an ending place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've reached my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention is a direction of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't achieve any goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you decided to keep going east.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So as long as you keep going east, your goal is already fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, are you going east?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've already achieved your goal to go east.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If your decision is to go the spiritual pathway, then you've already achieved that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What you mean is it's ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ultimate is what you're really talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All God asks of you is that you set the compass in a spiritually integrous direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else is asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not beneficial to have in this worldly form, in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say a direction, yes, an intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but that which we want to attain, that which we want to go to, not just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to actualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hold in mind a picture of what you feel would be the fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:06:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without desiring it, without trying to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You picture every place I've ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would picture what I picture would be ideal, but not crave it or want it or desire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And each time there would be a phone call and I would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,hey, the place next to me right along the creek is up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the only one I want to live next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so I came and looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of a little place out in the woods next to the creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing happened back east.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, you know, of acres of woods, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,building a certain kind of house in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to actualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's up to many karmic propensities and other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you unconsciously feel that you deserve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things have to be resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But it tends to come about as you picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But without trying to force it or make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's more like you picture that's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold it as a loving picture in your mind of what you admire or cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to let go of the solar plexus wantingness of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is to drive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With greed and kill everybody in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it over at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,are we free from suffering for all eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about all of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,human life is sickness, old age, suffering, and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's due to constantly recycling back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By identifying the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To transcend that illusion that you are the mind or that you are the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go of cravingness and wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Which binds you to the wheel of rebirth and reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let that go, you need not be reborn again in physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I never argued with a high thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've escaped the birth-death cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever suffer again after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, because Jesus, I thought after you became enlightened and escaped the karmic cycle, that life was eternal paradise, or you didn't have any more work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite get the gist of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to you after you're enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone for something to happen to, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're begging the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you are not anyone anymore, what happens to that one that is no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,End of problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After sugar dissolves in water, he doesn't have any problem with sugar anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been getting the impression, I guess, by reading partly Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharif Abdullah is one person that wrote a book recently that kind of states it very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's a definite threat to the biosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,From our overproduction and not watching out what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and also that part of the solution is a shift in myth to where we see that we're one family on one world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,away from the perception that we're all these separate nations and are against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you find any resonance with this, or is that something that's in your concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get the gist of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the gist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We see a coming problem with the earth, and that the solution is in the shift in the myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the way to be as a spiritual person is respectful of the sacredness of all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then from that respect for the sacredness of all of life, certain actions automatically follow that are aligned with that intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems that there's a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a crisis right now, and if we don't have a certain amount of increased spiritual perception of honoring the sacredness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we'll really have a bad mess-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the distribution of the consciousness level of mankind goes from,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,let's take the Green River pillar, probably around 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,call it ready consciousness of about 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes all the way up to 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, included in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, included in that immense straddle is all possibility, all possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I sort of answered your question earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was meant to be a celestial realm, it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither one of us would probably be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed to be a celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody who tries to impose their will on it and force it into being a celestial realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is following some kind of a spiritual illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage could be repaired in several more millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have a whole stratified set of choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's how we work out our karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a gymnasium, a school, a purgatorial opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the class, as a whole race, can go several steps back and have a long way back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or the class, as a whole race, can go squeeze through to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I think we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're different for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I had an experience much like the one you talked about in the snowbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:14:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And following that experience for three days, I felt somewhat assaulted by darker entities
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and felt, looking back, that I needed to stay in that physical space, within that eternal space,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the goal that I've been seeking, and left that physical space for reasons that I wasn't really aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It just kind of happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, although I've had a pretty significant shift of my sense of identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there still is a definite sense of ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, once that space is, or that state of consciousness is experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is it just a matter of remaining there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it seemed like there was a complete withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It usually doesn't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It usually doesn't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death experiences, transitory states of illumination, are usually not permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They usually come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But they inspire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you get a glimpse ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And they become inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think Ramana Maharishi, Nisargadatta Maharishi, all those will agree that in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,they may come as a state of illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christian literature of the saints is also full of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O my beloved, how couldst thou have left me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The angels, I mean, you know, the doves soaring, and then now down near the earth, feeling crestfallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you rise above your karma and go into a beatific state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then your negative karma catches up with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, one works harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's go wanting to return to that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget returning to that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it cannot be brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not volitional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not within the providence of will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the most spiritually pure life you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if providence sees, the grace of God so grants it, if your providence would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you rise above your karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you mentioned in your lecture that over 200, we come into this life with a particular karmic identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's also a predetermined exit moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we really don't need to have fear about that moment of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also talked about a few instances in your life when you were kind of at the turning point where it seemed like you could or when you were 14, you talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,possibly choosing to stay or to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard other people, you know, who had near death experiences talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hear from them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I mean, is, is it really completely predetermined?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are there instances where you actually do have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes our choice about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About whether to leave or to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave or stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As it seemed like you did when you were 14 and, and felt that your father wasn't ready to have you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, you neither win or lose, no matter which decision you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're really both the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that's very hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of whether a person's time of exit is predetermined, is that then, I guess it doesn't matter then you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it has to do with the intention at the time and the karmic propensities and whether that was one of your purposes in this reincarnation, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a rather complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And past life recall and all to get what the significance was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The choosing this was each time in the interest of love as love was understood at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the understanding of love to a 14 year old boy would be somewhat different than at age 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the comprehension, the way it's contextualized would be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, different karmic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If one case to say is sacrificial, another case to leave is sacrificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So do we have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The choice of sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can either breathe or not breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In that state, it's not necessary to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have absolute, total freedom to retain the body or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And because your mind is silent, you can't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the choosingness comes out of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's nothing but silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The choosingness happens of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't I that chose to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The choosingness chose to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is for a friend of mine who's turning 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's on the faculty and the board of directors of the Gestalt Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he read your book the first time, he was so moved by it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he bought a case and invited all the faculty to read this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I should say to so-and-so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To my dear friend, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's John Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,John Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like President?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Like President.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How about John?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only John Carter, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Carter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Cartier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean like Cartier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You state in your book that the Buddha taught enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and that Christ taught salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a distinction between the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvation is the celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibration is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment calibrates at 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,600 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like a more advanced destination to shoot for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also far more arduous and far less likely to be accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotusland Buddhism and Christianity are both like practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the negativity, the gravitation of the negativity on this planet is so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The provocation is so continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the media hits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with it constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallacy, rhetoric, distortion, positionality, emotional manipulation, glamorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ceaseless barrage that the likelihood of also leading an ordinary life and staying alive as a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and becoming enlightened is practically zilch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So Jesus says get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lotusland Buddhism says get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Become as pure a human being as you can and still live like a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Life and living so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's because of your alignment, your intention, devotion to Jesus Christ as your Savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he then becomes your advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might say the judges of justice hold on the scale, the weight of what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Christ speaks for you and says, but in my name did she ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So by that one is the benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The benefit of grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The grace of the Savior then is that he is the advocate for your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you left this lifetime, she may not have accomplished her ultimate goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but she has made a stated intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you merit admission to this celestial realm called heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.78,0:24:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be nobody there to be spoken for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first question has to do with the chakras.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.97,0:24:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if they, how they, or if they can be found on the, in the levels of consciousness, where would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, roughly comparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.46,0:24:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The base chakra, as I say, if you get down to the bottom of apathy, the energy has left the base chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.67,0:24:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just lay there in apathy, you don't even have the energy to feed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.21,0:24:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:24:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The base chakra is blown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.71,0:24:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.75,0:25:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You get up to higher levels, you get up to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.55,0:25:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.57,0:25:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.14,0:25:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Al-Qaeda operates out of the spleen, out of the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.11,0:25:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamas, all those operate out of the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.61,0:25:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the name of God, they kill, which is blasphemy, really, is actual blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They use the words of God against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.28,0:25:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, that which hates divinity masquerades that they are doing so in the name of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the ultimate blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.73,0:25:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they calibrate it at 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.64,0:25:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.65,0:25:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The solar plexus is wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say, you know, wantingness, aggressiveness, doingness, the capacity to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in the 200s, the 300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.93,0:25:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart, of course, is the heart chakra, the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.67,0:26:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The third eye, the opening of the third eye would be like 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.13,0:26:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.32,0:26:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Without kinesiology, people don't have spiritual discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't tell appearance from essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.74,0:26:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't tell the sheep's clothing from the wolf and the sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.59,0:26:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Jesus Christ sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.88,0:26:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, I want you to teach kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.97,0:26:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, people can tell whether it's a sheep or is it a wolf and sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.50,0:26:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because other than by their fruits you shall know them, there's no way of telling, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.85,0:26:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell a sheep from a wolf and sheep's clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.64,0:26:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sheep with wolf's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.05,0:26:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:26:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I scare people away so they won't find that I'm a sheep underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.23,0:27:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other question has to do with vibrational levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wonder, there's been a lot of work done around the organs of the body when they're running perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.11,0:27:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They run at 77 megahertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.16,0:27:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about frequency levels and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.70,0:27:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that when you pursue a spiritual path, there's a lot of talk about bringing your vibration up, bringing your frequency up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.22,0:27:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, is there any correlation?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.03,0:27:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a correlation or a bridge between that work and the work of the levels of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.24,0:27:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're talking about different scales of vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about spiritual energy and balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.11,0:27:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you're spiritually aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.81,0:27:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.01,0:27:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And your intentionality is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:28:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the chakra system and the acupuncture system will balance itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.81,0:28:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you have an impairment in some particular attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.85,0:28:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why John Diamond did such excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he found the acupuncture points that relate to certain attitudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.48,0:28:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would give you a, what do you call it, where you say positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.35,0:28:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.48,0:28:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.59,0:28:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An affirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.61,0:28:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, an affirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.18,0:28:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, you stimulate those specific acupuncture points.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.96,0:28:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those things that are related to body work and consciousness and attitudes are like a step between the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, body work is like a step between the physical and then the chakra system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.38,0:28:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the pure spiritual work, which doesn't pay attention to chakra systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.83,0:28:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure spiritual work doesn't pay attention to them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.74,0:28:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, esoterically, you could describe them, but they're irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.89,0:28:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the dagger's at the point of your enemy's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.29,0:29:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can either push it in or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't got time to do kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.69,0:29:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.15,0:29:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have time to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.19,0:29:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In one lifetime, you lose if you push it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.17,0:29:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In another lifetime, you lose if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.11,0:29:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.75,0:29:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, you can't know truth unless you know context.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.73,0:29:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity means crossing over 200 for integrity's reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.69,0:29:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as I've told other groups, one lifetime, I failed to kill a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.99,0:29:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.63,0:29:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.53,0:29:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came back and had to go through very painful surgery with no anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of it, I remembered the exact thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.03,0:29:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I put a sword right through his groin and did not give him the kudogra.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.77,0:29:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:29:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I left him to die of his wounds, which took him weeks of agony and fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.75,0:30:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I should have, one warrior to another, put him out of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.00,0:30:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to suffer the guilt of that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.61,0:30:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Agonizing that I had lacked the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.01,0:30:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One warrior to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.57,0:30:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In this war, you leave a pistol with one bullet left in it by his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.20,0:30:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.38,0:30:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's his choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.11,0:30:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's your obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior to warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.54,0:30:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in this lifetime, I did that karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.21,0:30:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I apologized to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.80,0:30:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I asked his forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.49,0:30:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have the courage to kudogra.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.75,0:30:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:30:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my love for him, I kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.82,0:30:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.45,0:30:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's intention, not the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.11,0:31:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in one lifetime, to run the dagger home would be cowardly and negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.70,0:31:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And another not to would be cowardly and negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.16,0:31:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, context makes the whole difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.00,0:31:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.71,0:31:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just have one other thing, which is I am so grateful for some of the things you said today about when you're born and when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.23,0:31:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And these things are all set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.10,0:31:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.82,0:31:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my first child in December, and she was only with us for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.58,0:31:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really can...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.06,0:31:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work has really helped with that, to know that these things are chosen, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically destined to come in and out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.03,0:31:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.53,0:31:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To experience the birth process for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And having accomplished it, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.76,0:31:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,End of karmic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.52,0:31:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.69,0:31:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.59,0:31:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Another interesting fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.14,0:31:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I like things that relieve guilt and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.14,0:31:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, is that the spirit, human spirit, doesn't enter the embryo until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.29,0:32:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.39,0:32:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.65,0:32:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit waits to make sure, I guess, the embryo is going to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.50,0:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't enter the human embryo until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.44,0:32:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.00,0:32:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.88,0:32:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.81,0:32:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, if I understood you correctly this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.27,0:32:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you had said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ came in in one lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.33,0:32:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And Edgar Cayce says that he was here 33 lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.70,0:32:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wondered why the discrepancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Cayce didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.54,0:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.43,0:32:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cayce was into the esoteric Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.25,0:32:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.20,0:32:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.70,0:32:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to be educated in esotericism.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.48,0:33:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the esoteric Christ, and then there's the physical material Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.16,0:33:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.24,0:33:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have permission to ask this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.79,0:33:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cayce was talking about the esoteric Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was speaking of the esoteric Christ, and not the actual physical Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.25,0:33:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Jesus the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to study...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.72,0:33:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her name that channeled the white brotherhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.69,0:33:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you read the Alice Bailey books, that'll sort of answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.26,0:33:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And Manley's books, which get more into esotericism.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.19,0:33:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.75,0:33:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.26,0:33:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.58,0:33:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are different levels of existence, other than the physical and the strictly spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.78,0:33:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Esoteric levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.13,0:33:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think Cayce was talking about the esoteric Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.71,0:33:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.59,0:33:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.75,0:33:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you might say was reborn again in the late 80s, when the consciousness level went
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.40,0:33:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from 190 to 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.66,0:34:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reemergence of the Christ consciousness, the second coming, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.75,0:34:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where they think another human being should come up and say, I'm reborn Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.81,0:34:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.46,0:34:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Christ consciousness prevails, then another wave of the Christ consciousness came
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.55,0:34:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in on October 14th at five in the afternoon, and it went from 205 to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.59,0:34:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me like the Christ consciousness prevails, then it increases, then it increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.94,0:34:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think would happen to the people on this planet if it went from 200 up to 1,000
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.65,0:34:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.11,0:34:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings sudden death to most people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.69,0:34:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.42,0:34:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.73,0:34:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You raise the level of the sea this much, then you raise the level of the sea this much
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.82,0:34:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because the whole world has to adjust to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.69,0:34:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual advancement is not supposed to be brutal, to force everybody to jump to 2,000
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.26,0:34:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or 1,000, I mean, to even go from 800 to 900, like fries your whole nervous system, like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.19,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd die 1,000 deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.32,0:35:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.32,0:35:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry everybody on the planet and force them to jump to 1,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.61,0:35:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.61,0:35:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Christ consciousness as...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.57,0:35:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.44,0:35:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes acceptable, moves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.84,0:35:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We may see another decade or a few decades, it moves another two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.48,0:35:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the upset that even a few points has caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.82,0:35:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All the giant corporations have fallen, all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.15,0:35:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads have been rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those heads would not have rolled at 190, and Ron would be profitable at 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.82,0:35:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.26,0:35:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.36,0:35:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to see them right now.
