Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.32,0:47:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say it's comparable to gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.71,0:47:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a primordial, the primordial energy out of which all of existence arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.88,0:47:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If divinity is primordial, infinite, formless energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.05,0:47:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it can, it then manifests.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.07,0:47:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It manifests as all of creation, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.23,0:47:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation then is expressed in different vibrational frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.63,0:47:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat, light, dark matter, light matter, dark hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.69,0:47:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark holes, dark galaxies, dark holes in the galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.42,0:47:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravitation is so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.48,0:47:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravitation in a dark hole is so intense that even light cannot escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:47:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gravity for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.30,0:48:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.69,0:48:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.32,0:48:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, your book has been very instrumental in a book that I'm writing right now
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.94,0:48:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,called The Science of Personal Fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.63,0:48:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been pursuing this for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.59,0:48:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But a question I want to ask is,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.51,0:48:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,do you consider yourself of the order of Melchizedek?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.57,0:48:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I consider myself what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.82,0:48:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the order of Melchizedek.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.25,0:48:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of Melchizedek?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.88,0:48:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.90,0:48:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that question because, you know, Jesus was of the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.98,0:48:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was a healer, which you are also.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.26,0:49:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I say he was a healer, I mean the energy field that surrounded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.78,0:49:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never contextualized it in that way because I didn't contextualize Jesus Christ either.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.19,0:49:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.44,0:49:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual contextualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.76,0:49:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One I'm not familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.51,0:49:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand what you're saying now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.38,0:49:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.23,0:49:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.80,0:49:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.48,0:49:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wrestling with one of my basic instincts that is anger that I'm seeking to subdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.36,0:49:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And my fiancée, well aware of that, she does things to bring it out and elevate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.51,0:49:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when I tell her, I say, well, look, a man and a woman are supposed to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.98,0:49:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are certain thoughts that I wouldn't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.21,0:49:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even think knowing what it would do to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.75,0:50:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were supposed to be part of me doing these things to bring these things out of me that I'm trying to subdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.36,0:50:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the other hand, she's telling me, well, if you are studying that, you're supposed to be able to do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.25,0:50:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm, you know, I sit thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.61,0:50:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.38,0:50:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's giving you all these golden opportunities, in other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.13,0:50:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.07,0:50:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.07,0:50:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.03,0:50:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have given me the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.30,0:50:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The opportunity to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.82,0:50:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.73,0:50:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I take the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.23,0:50:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.19,0:50:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, look, no, I say, I don't think, you know, you are being part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.00,0:50:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.01,0:50:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.07,0:50:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.88,0:50:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, she's part of you, but with limitations, with reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.76,0:50:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.32,0:50:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.55,0:50:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If God meant for there to be one sex, there would be one sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.98,0:50:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.50,0:50:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There would only be one sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.28,0:51:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A female sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.34,0:51:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A butterfly has two wings to fly with, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.19,0:51:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.57,0:51:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.03,0:51:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.48,0:51:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, you spoke about how when we're born, we're already at a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.15,0:51:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.86,0:51:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which also means we're already at a particular karmic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.71,0:51:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.69,0:51:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.21,0:51:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As our life progresses and we make choices...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.73,0:51:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes people make negative choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.17,0:51:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.36,0:51:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.84,0:51:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our life kind of like a yo-yo in terms of spiritual growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.76,0:51:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we not...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.76,0:51:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's life is not an upward progression, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.00,0:51:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.23,0:51:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.17,0:51:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people in this lifetime have fallen considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.38,0:52:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do Napoleon, Napoleon was about 450, 460, and he became emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.57,0:52:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown himself emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.15,0:52:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His calibration then dropped to about 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.71,0:52:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,130 or 160 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.09,0:52:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of the Battle of Waterloo, the Duke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.48,0:52:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duke of Wellington calibrated around, don't forget, 420 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.11,0:52:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But by that time, Napoleon had crashed and was like about 170.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.82,0:52:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Hitler also calibrated in reasonably good 400s early in his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.71,0:52:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And when...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.96,0:52:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can, with kinesiology, track historically when these events happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.57,0:52:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With Napoleon, it was when he...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.51,0:52:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He crowned himself emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.61,0:52:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See, to crown the sovereign head of a European state was done by the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.05,0:53:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So he usurped the pope and crowned himself emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.90,0:53:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that moment, he crashed into megalomania.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.78,0:53:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler did the same thing when he became head of all the departments of government.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.17,0:53:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the head of the army, the head of the military, the head of the government, the head of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.28,0:53:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that moment, Hitler crashed from four...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty or wherever he was, down to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.65,0:53:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was when he finally gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.63,0:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that narcissistic megalomania lies in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.48,0:53:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.82,0:53:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the grandiosity then destroys what could have been great.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.57,0:53:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Winston Churchill did not succumb to the same temptation, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.30,0:53:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So power then, worthly power, differentiates the sheep from the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.69,0:53:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You either become a statesman...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.86,0:53:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.76,0:53:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you become a megalomaniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.23,0:54:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.67,0:54:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you asked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.90,0:54:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.32,0:54:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.80,0:54:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one of the things that has happened to me since I've been reading your book
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.07,0:54:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is I'm constantly looking at the numbers and saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.88,0:54:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, where would I fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.19,0:54:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and I don't know if other people are doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.61,0:54:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about where you fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.96,0:54:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in other words, it's a kind of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.88,0:54:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You already are what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.76,0:54:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.19,0:54:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because unless you were spiritually...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.98,0:54:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrous, you wouldn't be on a spiritual pathway to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.80,0:54:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're on a spiritual pathway, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.82,0:54:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.30,0:54:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Jesus worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.55,0:54:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he's there for.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.21,0:54:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.23,0:54:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.25,0:54:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you were talking about Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.78,0:54:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,were you saying Jesus was an advocate?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.09,0:54:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You used the word advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.84,0:54:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.80,0:54:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spokesman for on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.09,0:54:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stand before the Father in your behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.32,0:54:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have aligned yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.36,0:54:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have aligned yourself with me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.84,0:55:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and in my name, in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.05,0:55:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.94,0:55:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Lord Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.32,0:55:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will look after these are my...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.15,0:55:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these are my sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.76,0:55:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They have committed to me karmically.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.61,0:55:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They are now my sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.94,0:55:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I speak for them on their behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.28,0:55:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will look after them, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.13,0:55:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Lord says, pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.90,0:55:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.71,0:55:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where does grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.03,0:55:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.82,0:55:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.50,0:55:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does grace come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.15,0:55:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.84,0:55:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.26,0:55:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace is a very sophisticated understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.21,0:55:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by grace that you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.88,0:55:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by grace that you are allowed to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.44,0:55:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the consequences of wrong decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.61,0:55:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by grace that you can earn karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.05,0:55:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.15,0:55:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.03,0:56:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.63,0:56:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by grace that you can undo the errors of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.25,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by grace that you have existence in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.19,0:56:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.48,0:56:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.34,0:56:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.15,0:56:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think grace probably answered my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.94,0:56:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question was about karmic consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.65,0:56:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for choosing to have an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.59,0:56:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.55,0:56:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.34,0:56:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That would depend on the individual
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.82,0:56:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the context in which it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.63,0:56:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned before
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.67,0:56:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit doesn't come into the embryo
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.17,0:56:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.36,0:56:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.71,0:56:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's an abortion within the first three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.28,0:56:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the person is technically guilty of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.03,0:56:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no spirit there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.94,0:56:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the primordial embryonic animalness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.73,0:57:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that is going to be inherited by a human spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.71,0:57:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on many factors, intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.46,0:57:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.73,0:57:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first I had ever heard of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.28,0:57:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the human spirit not coming into the human embryo
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.59,0:57:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,until the third month when you said that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.40,0:57:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.98,0:57:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.48,0:57:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, I've carried a lot of guilt and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.57,0:57:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I hope to God it was before three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.90,0:57:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, spontaneous abortions are so frequent
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.46,0:57:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that people don't even know they happen that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.55,0:57:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They think it's a missed period.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.01,0:57:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.98,0:57:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.63,0:57:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably 10% of all pregnancies end up in spontaneous abortion,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.42,0:57:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe more, maybe closer to a third.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.59,0:57:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they skipped a period, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.44,0:57:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.96,0:57:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneous miscarriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.67,0:57:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So would they have to do with also, like, the soul coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.38,0:58:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was that soul's purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.42,0:58:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.94,0:58:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.17,0:58:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew how to do kinesiology very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.59,0:58:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you get permission, you could ask many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.82,0:58:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this spirit only mean to come in and leave right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.59,0:58:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have accomplished that spirit's purpose, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.21,0:58:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're feeling guilty about nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.55,0:58:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when actually that was the spirit's purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.84,0:58:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.67,0:58:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.44,0:58:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got to research it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.48,0:58:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, yeah, a question for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.25,0:58:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but also, if, I mean, I think it was before three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.48,0:58:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but if it wasn't, so karmically, you're, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.82,0:58:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is that like, you'd most likely play that out in another lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.17,0:58:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.42,0:58:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.76,0:58:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.55,0:58:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.63,0:58:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you might come in and get aborted too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.46,0:58:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I was thinking, or, you know, to have that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.30,0:58:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyways, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.86,0:59:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.57,0:59:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.86,0:59:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to have faith that it all works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.46,0:59:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, God's will prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.38,0:59:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, God's will prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.69,0:59:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you feel guilt about it, you ask for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.36,0:59:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've made a mistake, then I pray for forgiveness of the mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.57,0:59:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.38,0:59:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.82,0:59:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the end, God's will prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.98,0:59:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, God's goodness prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.92,0:59:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you haven't held up the progress of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.78,0:59:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.34,0:59:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to exaggerate the importance of our mistakes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.73,0:59:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In the overall course of the evolution of the universe, it's trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.34,0:59:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.01,0:59:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking my question, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.94,0:59:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I understand what you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.32,0:59:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it would seem as though the time of our death is predetermined from the time that we hit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.88,1:00:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment you're born,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.09,1:00:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment of your death is already predetermined.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.34,1:00:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where we go to kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.92,1:00:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not putting money there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.69,1:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I learned, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.98,1:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that being the case, what does that say about safety concerns,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.53,1:00:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or you alluded to skydiving, or even free will,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.23,1:00:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the choice to take one's own life if there was a severe illness or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.96,1:00:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.86,1:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there free will in that matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.55,1:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's free will.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.36,1:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose to die or not to die, that's not going to determine what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.32,1:00:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you get your, you get to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.63,1:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I understand that it's predetermined, but I still get to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.86,1:00:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.96,1:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The time, you can't control.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.38,1:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you do have the capacity to influence the way in which it may happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.15,1:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.44,1:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that if I were a person who was in a nursing home and I was ill and decided,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.13,1:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I would have that ability still.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.71,1:01:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.98,1:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.63,1:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to leave the,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.36,1:01:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to leave at the time that you're destined to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.86,1:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would presume the old lady in the wheelchair who can't get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.65,1:01:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's not time for her yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.98,1:01:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time, you can't stop her from getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.48,1:01:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a karmic consequence to suicide?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.03,1:01:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really researched the karmic consequence of suicide,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.82,1:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not as down as people think.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.38,1:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember who was that lady that wrote so much, the doctor, about death and dying?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.92,1:01:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kubler-Ross.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.44,1:01:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubler-Ross, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.59,1:01:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In her research,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.44,1:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,suicide didn't appear to have any negative, a real negative consequence at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.84,1:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.46,1:02:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And why should God care about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.76,1:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to check yourself out?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.15,1:02:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.82,1:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you comment on capital punishment?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.26,1:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.13,1:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital punishment calibrates over 30, 35, about 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.90,1:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.76,1:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.78,1:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.28,1:02:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking about spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.13,1:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, doesn't that an attention doesn't fluctuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.90,1:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet there seems to be an experience often called the dark night of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.55,1:02:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.55,1:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.55,1:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you like, but you're not necessarily dropping to that as an overall.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.76,1:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you know, you've read, you read all the Christian saints and many have written about the dark night of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.65,1:03:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have it more.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.65,1:03:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the Christians and others, you don't read so much about the dark night of the soul coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.38,1:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,India or Buddhism is not really a familiar thing in Buddhist literature.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.09,1:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more in Christian literature.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.30,1:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you transcend all your dark karma, go into a great place.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.36,1:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now your negative karma, the undone comes up, takes you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.30,1:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So negative karma of the undone, the undone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.80,1:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.30,1:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've transcended up to there, but there's farther to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.94,1:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And now because you're not in now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.01,1:03:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've brought up is stuff that would not have been brought up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.46,1:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you not risen to that level, you're not going to have a problem with forgiveness until you really do the course of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.53,1:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And now forgiveness is the biggest problem in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.84,1:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you see everything in terms of the kind of nation you're okay until you set a higher spiritual goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.98,1:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've brought your bottom up, brought up your bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.90,1:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See, so you used to be able to hate bad people and it was no problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.36,1:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you're guilt stricken.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.36,1:04:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see ludicrous as an okay guy in that tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.55,1:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I going to see ludicrous as an okay guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.59,1:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about how they call hollow point bullets, kicking pregnant wives in the belly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.92,1:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to love this guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.46,1:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See what a problem I got now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.78,1:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't have that problem before I did the course of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.51,1:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was a swell guy or else I hated him, but I didn't have any problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.57,1:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you do this, all right, so spiritual evolution itself will not keep giving you new problems that will take you out of euphoria when you're over your, when you're, when you're, um, ahead of your karma, you feel euphoric, but then that doesn't last because the next lesson comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.86,1:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.53,1:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't mean you've fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.19,1:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you're still advancing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.65,1:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.34,1:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop advancing, you probably go back to the euphoria again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.03,1:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll continue to feel so long as you're ahead of your karma, see, but the spirit doesn't allow you to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.94,1:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the spirit says, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.53,1:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.46,1:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, cause I, cause I did the course of miracles for a really long time and it felt like I cut out a whole level and hit a point of grace for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.07,1:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's like all the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.80,1:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.19,1:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or like that's from past lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.28,1:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.71,1:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.07,1:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.57,1:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking up is from past lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.57,1:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.73,1:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The past lifetimes are catching up with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.40,1:05:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.38,1:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's, I mean, that's good because I can then move through them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.82,1:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.65,1:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.48,1:06:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Buddha said he was beset by demons, you know, beset by demons.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.98,1:06:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lifetime, I've been fried by them, you know, fry your nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.71,1:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,God Almighty, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.15,1:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand like, cause it always felt like I'd done something wrong because I know that as you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.84,1:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you draw to you and then to suddenly hit such a bottom, it's like, oh, what did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.88,1:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You become a challenge to the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.76,1:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.96,1:06:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You become a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.01,1:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The forces that prevail due to lack of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.40,1:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as you evolve, you become a threat to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.61,1:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run in round the way you run in round, but when the integrity level jumps over 205, you can't run and run that way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.11,1:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.67,1:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.23,1:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.00,1:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Real calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.57,1:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost through.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.21,1:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.92,1:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to quit at six.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.61,1:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.07,1:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.86,1:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, Dr. Ian Stevenson, University of Virginia, psychiatrist, age probably about 82 or 83 now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.40,1:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the early 70s, he did a book called 20 Cases Suggestive of Reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.34,1:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, he had checked memories of kids throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.86,1:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.51,1:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, about.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.57,1:07:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.15,1:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, he's up at about 7,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.69,1:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.03,1:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A book called Old Souls, written by the editor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.86,1:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, trying to document reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.17,1:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.86,1:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I met him some years ago when he had just written the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.96,1:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was still in manuscript form when I was, well, on the West Coast.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.96,1:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I asked him, when does the soul usually enter the body?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.82,1:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.51,1:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, at birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.71,1:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost always at birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.84,1:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, there's a little delay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.48,1:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a day or two, a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.30,1:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.46,1:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the soul enter, I asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.26,1:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forget the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.86,1:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.92,1:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, almost always through the soft part of the skull.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.56,1:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fontanelle, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.63,1:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're coming up with three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.17,1:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I get with kinesiology when I ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.94,1:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.31,1:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.55,1:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In light of Ian Stevenson, the soul enters at birth?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.56,1:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul enters.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.27,1:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this in front of this audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.55,1:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
