Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.69,1:08:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.80,1:08:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see him answering.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.18,1:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then we have a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.34,1:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because you see, the spirit is the etheric body, and the etheric body is not physical,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.92,1:08:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so it doesn't enter the brain in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.77,1:08:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.19,1:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.76,1:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it doesn't need a fontanelle because it's not physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.64,1:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the soul is a much broader kind of part of oneself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.55,1:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.78,1:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.14,1:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stevenson's singing about it in more,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.09,1:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,physical terms, that it's probably more like a diffuse field, probably more like a diffuse
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.51,1:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,field.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.96,1:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.98,1:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard of this name in a long time, Ian Stevenson.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.77,1:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.84,1:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are in a situation that seems to be difficult where the environment may be at
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.26,1:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a lower consciousness level than you are, and I'm thinking in particular of a job I
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.93,1:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,have, what's the best way to be able to hold on to your own level of consciousness and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.30,1:09:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not be pulled down?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.30,1:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't pull down except with your agreement.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.65,1:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's a lower level of consciousness than your own, then it's a test pattern you're
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.14,1:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.38,1:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we aggravate her enough, she'll finally hate us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.52,1:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.52,1:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After you pass the test, it'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.72,1:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like looking for your weak spots.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.76,1:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We aggravate her enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.76,1:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, she'll hate us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.14,1:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They will get her to hate us, and she will no longer become an enemy of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.14,1:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll enjoy the haters of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.13,1:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you resist that and make a choice, it will disappear from your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.90,1:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It will have served a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.90,1:10:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is like...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.93,1:10:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll be surrounded with nice people.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.93,1:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.31,1:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a test period in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.14,1:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just keep returning negativity with positive happiness and good and blessings
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.09,1:10:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera, it will disappear from your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.09,1:10:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.22,1:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.35,1:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be nothing to hold it in place anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.96,1:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being held in place by the test pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.35,1:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.93,1:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I wanted to ask you, what is the nature of true service?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.10,1:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.03,1:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,True service?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.03,1:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Service to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.03,1:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that would take all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.09,1:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But, briefly, it is to surrender one's personal willfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.09,1:11:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.76,1:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 12 steps, I think, are very end-all, so they're very important.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.56,1:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.56,1:11:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the course of miracles, to surrender one's self, one's life to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.47,1:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.47,1:11:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as time goes on, you realize that you never did know what it means, because it's
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.76,1:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,revealed to you differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.76,1:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes through a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.28,1:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're supposed to surrender to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.44,1:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.72,1:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To even know what that means probably takes a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.72,1:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what the will of God means, then, comes as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.82,1:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it means one thing at this level, one thing at this level, one thing at this level,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.82,1:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing at this level.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.82,1:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, when it's served its purpose at this level, it takes on a new meaning at the next
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.56,1:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.56,1:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to follow up to that, the reason I ask that, sometimes it feels like there's
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.06,1:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,an overwhelming sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.06,1:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.06,1:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering, is that the unworthiness of the ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.06,1:12:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The unworthiness of the ego, or the aspiration of the soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.06,1:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a combination of both.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.06,1:12:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With prayer, you get the illumination of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.06,1:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get illumination.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.57,1:12:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You just say, Dear God, I ask out of your kindness and beneficence for clarification
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.11,1:12:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of this understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.11,1:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.11,1:12:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.85,1:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as you're driving down the road, it's a snap.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.31,1:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
